			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">AT THE RANCH, TOWN AND DATA SCREEN CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Select icon:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
