                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Advance pages (during Data Screen Competition):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Go back pages (during Data Screen Competition):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Quit menu:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause the game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BATTLE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move monster:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change fighting technique:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Knock enemy away:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move cursor to move to different fighting technique:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 and R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause the game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>
